text: Milan Škopek (born 22 January 1959) is a Czech rower. He competed at the 1980 Summer Olympics and the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Czechoslovakia Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Prague
